    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I don't think we change it. Browsers collapse adjacent whitespace when displaying HTML. I think this is actually part of the official HTML specification.\r\n\r\nIf you want to use multiple spaces without them collapsing, you can use `&nbsp;` (non-breaking space), or control it using CSS (https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/pr_text_white-space.asp).\r\n\r\n"
  },
